{"tid":1175975,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★新移民婦 盼撤綜援金居港條件","createTime":"2019-05-29T02:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T02:55:53.000Z","uid":21598,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3fb9d56a016d96e994d016cde8a7398d8bc61f","tid":1175975,"uid":21598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20110207/large/07la7p15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20110207%2Flarge%2F07la7p15.jpg&h=6f0b92d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿娥表示，女兒的綜援有近半要用作交租，生活拮据。 <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】新移民數目越來越多，部份來港後因各種原因成了單親家庭，經濟問題無法解決。社區組織協會花一年訪問 57名來港不足七年的新移民婦女，逾八成受訪者曾申請綜援，但當中只有四成最終在酌情權下獲批。近四成受訪者曾因不獲綜援萌輕生念頭，她們認為政府應取消申請綜援須居港七年的條件，同時取消單親媽媽要工作不少於 120小時或月入不少於 1,630元的限制。 <br />\n「 11蚊三份餸食兩日」 <br />\n<br />\n社協進行調查，逾八成受訪者子女有領取綜援，六成受訪者現時沒有工作，當中 37人為單親媽媽。約六成媽媽因居港未滿七年而未能獲批綜援，生活出現困難，她們只能減少開支，甚至向他人借貸或進食過期食物度日。 72%感到因新移民身份而備受歧視， 38%受訪者甚至想過自殺。去年來港的新移民阿娥， 08年與港人丈夫誕下一女，丈夫 09病逝，來港後只能靠近 3,000元子女綜援及津貼過日子：「屋租都用咗 1,500蚊，街市 11蚊三份餸食兩日，試過抱住個女喺公園喊足兩個鐘。」「我哋都係香港人，唔應該對新移民唔公平。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6wOvQBg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wOvQBg.gif&h=80039f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n【民陣6.9反惡法遊行】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n反對逃犯條例白宮聯署<br />\n-簽完記得確認返電郵<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fextradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2IV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=36affe2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/extradition-law-amendment-hong-kong-threat-personal-safety-and-freedom</a>"},{"pid":"7e7cbb89d848e53365b5d7bf53933b5bce465eb7","tid":1175975,"uid":223525,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"無錢學人移民叫難民"},{"pid":"61d246bce6844fad6086fa56cfe154a2ea2940f1","tid":1175975,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e7cbb89d848e53365b5d7bf53933b5bce465eb7","tid":1175975,"uid":223525,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"無錢學人移民叫難民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:13:00.000Z","msg":"無錢學人生仔叫仆街"},{"pid":"196a170c9e8555d67edd2f6dfc8b504448cad38c","tid":1175975,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:16:16.000Z","msg":"出錢買子彈幫佢哋打靶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77387bd150ddbf2985ccc0804d6faaede35c3704","tid":1175975,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:21:31.000Z","msg":"無能力咪返大灣區囉屌妳班賤種。"},{"pid":"58073f6aeff81f86ee66e7ebd785e2129033dd80","tid":1175975,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:30:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支那雞  大陸閪</span></span>"},{"pid":"c2e35968fc4184a789e5ca1d4a939e56dfbbd7e4","tid":1175975,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:31:24.000Z","msg":"帶埋啲幼蟲返上去囉&hellip;"},{"pid":"dc3ce6933509257fc55a63fa848f547297780d94","tid":1175975,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"應該驅逐佢地出境"},{"pid":"7af9dba14ac0b822d813e87f855f73143976d2d1","tid":1175975,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:32:19.000Z","msg":"咁嚟香港做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa86be57fd835e47753d62722ad8b2dd64840351","tid":1175975,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T02:55:53.00